optional_parameters.name: sort
optional_parameters.description:
For `status_type` = `ForSale` OR `RecentlySold` are available:
- `Homes_for_You`
- `Price_High_Low`
- `Price_Low_High`
- `Newest`
- `Bedrooms`
- `Bathrooms`
- `Square_Feet`
- `Lot_Size`

default `Homes_for_You`

For `status_type` = `ForRent` are available:
- `Verified_Source`
- `Payment_High_Low`
- `Payment_Low_High`
- `Newest`
- `Bedrooms`
- `Bathrooms`
- `Square_Feet`
- `Lot_Size`

default `Verified_Source`

optional_parameters.name: page
optional_parameters.description: Page number if at the previous response `totalPages` > 1

optional_parameters.name: home_type
optional_parameters.description:

- `Multi-family`
- `Apartments`
- `Houses`
- `Manufactured`
- `Condos`
- `LotsLand`
- `Townhomes`
